RAD_DATASOURCES.RELATION_WITH_PARENT: OLTBS_CONTRACT_SPLIT_ROLLOVER.CONTRACT_REF_NO = OLTBS_CONTRACT_ROLL_INT_RATES.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND OLTBS_CONTRACT_SPLIT_ROLLOVER.VERSION_NO = OLTBS_CONTRACT_ROLL_INT_RATES.VERSION_NO AND OLTBS_CONTRACT_SPLIT_ROLLOVER.SPLIT_NO = OLTBS_CONTRACT_ROLL_INT_RATES.SPLIT_NO

RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT DRAWDOWN_NO,DRAWDOWN_CCY_AMOUNT FROM LBTBS_DRAWDOWN_SCHEDULE WHERE TRANCHE_REF_NO = (Select tranche_ref_no from oltbs_contract_master where contract_ref_no= ? and version_no = ?) and DRAWDOWN_TYPE = 'R' and RENEWAL_TYPE = 'S' and nvl(associated,'N')='N' and drawdown_ccy = (select contract_ccy from oltbs_contract where contract_ref_no= ? and version_no = ?) and drawdown_date =(select maturity_date from oltbs_contract_master where contract_ref_no = ? and version_no = ?) and borrower = (select counterparty from oltbs_contract where contract_ref_no = ? and version_no = ?) and drawdown_product = sypks_utils.get_product(?) MINUS SELECT DRAWDOWN_NO,MAX_ROLL_AMOUNT FROM OLTBS_CONTRACT_SPLIT_ROLLOVER WHERE contract_ref_no = ? AND VERSION_NO=(SELECT MAX(VERSION_NO) FROM OLTBS_CONTRACT_SPLIT_ROLLOVER WHERE contract_ref_no = ?)

SELECT DISTINCT A.RATE_CODE, A.RATE_DESCR FROM CFTMS_RATE_CODE A, CFTMS_FLOAT_RATE_MASTER B WHERE A.RATE_CODE = B.RATE_CODE AND A.RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND A.AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND A.BRANCH_CODE = sypks_utils.get_branch(?) AND A.BRANCH_CODE = B.BRANCH_CODE AND 'F' = ? UNION SELECT RATE_CODE,RATE_CODE_DESC FROM LFTMS_STANDARD_RATE_CODE WHERE RATE_TYPE='S' AND RECORD_STAT='O' AND AUTH_STAT='A' AND 'X' = ? UNION SELECT DISTINCT RATE_CODE, RATE_DESCR FROM CFTMS_RFR_MASTER WHERE RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A'
SELECT Component FROM lftms_product_iccf WHERE product = ? AND nvl(stop_application,'N') = 'N'

RAD_DATASOURCES.RELATION_WITH_PARENT: OLTBS_CONTRACT_ROLL_INT_RATES.CONTRACT_REF_NO = LFTB_CONT_ADDL_INT_DTL.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND OLTBS_CONTRACT_ROLL_INT_RATES.VERSION_NO = LFTB_CONT_ADDL_INT_DTL.VERSION_NO AND OLTBS_CONTRACT_ROLL_INT_RATES.SPLIT_NO = LFTB_CONT_ADDL_INT_DTL.SPLIT_SERIAL_NO AND OLTBS_CONTRACT_ROLL_INT_RATES.COMPONENT = LFTB_CONT_ADDL_INT_DTL.COMPONENT
